{
  "page": "Westermen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e9/Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png/350px-Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"224\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e9/Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png/525px-Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e9/Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png/700px-Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Andrew_Hall_Western_Fiefdoms.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Western Fiefdoms by Andrew Hall © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Westermen</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> are natives of the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>, a western region of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Ethnicity\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Ethnicity</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Culture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Culture</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Religion\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Religion</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Customs\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Customs</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Ethnicity\">Ethnicity</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westermen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Ethnicity\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Joffrey_Doggett.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f9/Joffrey_Doggett.jpg/350px-Joffrey_Doggett.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"302\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f9/Joffrey_Doggett.jpg/525px-Joffrey_Doggett.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f9/Joffrey_Doggett.jpg/700px-Joffrey_Doggett.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Joffrey_Doggett.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Doggett\" title=\"Joffrey Doggett\">Joffrey Doggett</a> by Douglas Wheatley ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> were settled in antiquity by the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a>, who drove out <a href=\"/index.php/Giants\" title=\"Giants\">giants</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a> and established numerous petty kingdoms in the region.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The most powerful of them were the <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_of_the_Rock\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kings of the Rock\">Kings of the Rock</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>. Rather than oppose the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to the west, the Lannister kings arranged marriages with <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> and integrated the powerful newcomers into their realm. When King <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_III_Lannister\" title=\"Gerold III Lannister\">Gerold III Lannister</a> died without male issue, a council crowned his daughter's husband, Ser Joffrey Lydden, who became the first Andal King of the Rock, <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Lannister\" title=\"Joffrey Lannister\">Joffrey Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westermen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Religion\">Religion</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westermen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Religion\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg/350px-Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg/525px-Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7b/Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg/700px-Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Thomas_Denmark_tywin_jaime.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>, by Thomas Denmark © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Brought to <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_arrival_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> is the predominant religion in the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a> has a great <a href=\"/index.php/Motherhouse\" title=\"Motherhouse\">motherhouse</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Customs\">Customs</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westermen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Customs\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> are known for their deposits of <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a>, with <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> having the richest gold mines in the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Wealthy <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> is renowned for its goldwork and goldsmiths.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Westermen and <a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">rivermen</a> of yore referred to the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> as \"<a href=\"/index.php/Wolves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wolves\">wolves</a> of the sea\",<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> and the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Farman\" title=\"House Farman\">Farmans</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a> are famous for their hatred of the ironmen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The customary surname of <a href=\"/index.php/Bastardy\" title=\"Bastardy\">bastards</a> of noble origin born in the westerlands is Hill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westermen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The great wealth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>, of course, stems primarily from their <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> mines. The veins of ore run wide and deep, and there are mines, even now, that have been delved for a thousand years and more and are yet to be emptied.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Westermen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 26\">Chapter 26</a>, Arya VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7